71,"uid":90827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7e29482bbcca6c7155b402f9fab7555afee51c5","tid":1426371,"uid":22465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:15:46.000Z","msg":"上個月去完，有食定藥，完全無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲藥用淨好多（獨立包裝），需要既可以比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:58:54.000Z","msg":"咩藥？係香港同埋係瑞士買唔買到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:44:33.000Z","msg":"香港買到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:10:42.000Z","msg":"就咁去藥房話買高山症藥物就得？"},{"pid":"1f4d1ffb7a8c1d80b34b74c1b3f32e9383911671","tid":1426371,"uid":22465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2a6ccb0a9c35cfde357c814006b1c7e6454368d","tid":1426371,"uid":90827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3b3f027071bd85633f870058b2d61ba80d59d9e","tid":1426371,"uid":22465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ed0cd1f29028eab6c2dc4786afe67b541a856f8","tid":1426371,"uid":90827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:58:54.000Z","msg":"咩藥？係香港同埋係瑞士買唔買到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:44:33.000Z","msg":"香港買到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:10:42.000Z","msg":"就咁去藥房話買高山症藥物就得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:11:34.000Z","msg":"係，但佢一買成盒買，用唔晒的"},{"pid":"067ba153ee4804be65216e3ceb5fdceb64df03e5","tid":1426371,"uid":40133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:15:55.000Z","msg":"回樓主<br />\n最好搵家庭醫生問問<br />\n一般人上到2000米就會有高反<br />\n可以事前食定藥，隻藥叫Diamox ，印象中係要醫生處方，但有副作用，會手腳指麻痺，尿頻。我自己就會塊面都麻痺。<br />\n加上你有哮喘底，山上氣溫一凍就好易出事，記得帶定哮喘噴藥<br />\n<br />\n所以最好問一問家庭醫生"},{"pid":"dd4d7091988116e231abbb1761bd6526b54feddc","tid":1426371,"uid":137424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:15:42.000Z","msg":"前幾日先上完真係會頭暈，最衰架火車係限指定班次，如果唔係要排長龍等吉位先落到山。"},{"pid":"700faf504796072bba314ae5576b69c3bd3160a4","tid":1426371,"uid":260202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:56:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.travelhealth.gov.hk/tc_chi/environmental_health_risk/high_altitude.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.travelhealth.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fenvironmental_health_risk%2Fhigh_altitude.html&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apJmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=082e76e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.travelhealth.gov.hk/tc_chi/environmental_health_risk/high_altitude.html</a><br />\n如病徵輕微，應嘗試減少體力活動，於同一高度逗留一至兩天直至病徵消失，然後才可繼續登山。<br />\n如病徵持續超過24小時或趨於嚴重，下山返回較低位置是最有效的治療方法，下降五百至一千米便可。<br />\n除Diamox, 必理痛都要帶定舒緩頭痛"}]}